title: Couple With Heart: Man, Person, Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple With Heart: Man, Person, Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A couple composed of a man and a person, with a heart between them, and specified with medium-dark skin tones. Represents romantic love and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this heartwarming emoji portrays a couple in a loving embrace, with one figure identified as a man and the other a gender-neutral person with a medium-dark skin tone, encircled by a vibrant red heart. Apple’s signature glossy 3D shading and soft rounded edges give the figures a tender, approachable appearance and make the heart feel almost tangible. This emoji on Apple devices is a beautiful representation of romantic love, partnership, and deep affection between two individuals.
